The '''Vietnam Institute of Archaeology''' ({{lang-vi|Viện khảo cổ học}}) is an important archaeological institution in [[Vietnam]]. It is based in [[Hanoi]]. The institute has been responsible for the coordination of many notable archaeological finds in the country.

